til has_more is false.","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#operation-v1-badges-get","method":"get","path":"/v1/badges","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Endpoints"},{"title":"Read the public receipt index.","content":"Cursor-paginated list response. Use pagination.next_url until has_more is false.","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#operation-v1-receipts-get","method":"get","path":"/v1/receipts","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Endpoints"},{"title":"Read one public receipt","content":"Returns the public payload snapshot plus an explicit integrity classification: externally anchored, source verified only, or public record only.","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#operation-v1-receipts-code-get","method":"get","path":"/v1/receipts/{code}","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Endpoints"},{"title":"Read the Arena wanted board and blotter.","content":"Cursor-paginated list response. Use pagination.next_url until has_more is false.","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#operation-v1-arena-get","method":"get","path":"/v1/arena","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Endpoints"},{"title":"Read public surface health and status lines. all_ok is deliberately strict: it is false when any line is in watch state.","content":"","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#operation-v1-status-get","method":"get","path":"/v1/status","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Endpoints"},{"title":"Read one bounty","content":"","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#operation-v1-bounties-id-get","method":"get","path":"/v1/bounties/{id}","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Endpoints"},{"title":"PublicBoardResponse","content":"","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#definition-publicboardresponse","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Models"},{"title":"PublicLedgerResponse","content":"","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#definition-publicledgerresponse","tab":"Public Overview","category":"Models"},{"title":"PublicBountyResponse","content":"","url":"/frantic-board/overview.html#definition-publicbountyrespo